item.foolish.battle_fan.description_0: §7Left-click within the general vicinity of a mob to launch them in the direction you swing.
item.foolish.battle_fan.description_1: §7Right-click the sides of blocks to launch yourself
item.foolish.blazing_pitchfork.descripti: §7Tosses mobs into the air and ignites them
§7Right-click to jump and shoot a fireball downwards
item.foolish.boneweaver_sword.descriptio: §7Right-click to channel the blade upwards and spawn a Chronosand Twister.
§7Grants speed boost when on Chronosand blocks.
item.foolish.burn_stinger.description_0: §7Awards more positive effects to the user and negative effects, including fire, to the target
item.foolish.charged_gauntlet.descriptio: §7Hit multiple mobs to temporarily charge them
§7Right-click to strike all charged mobs with lightning
§7If a mob's charge expires naturally, it will take damage.
item.foolish.charm_of_carnage.descriptio: §7Activate in the Nether to summon and fight the Wendigrudge.
item.foolish.florasabre_rapier.descripti: §7Sneak and left-click to retreat, right-click to lunge and deal heavy damage.
item.foolish.foolish_logo.description_3: §7Resistance + saturation / sneak to give night vision
item.foolish.four_x_extender.description: §7No building mod? Hate building walls? Extends a block up 4.
item.foolish.hand_of_time_sword.descript: §7Sneak and Right-Click while dual-wielding Minute Form combine them into Hour Form
§7Right-Click without sneaking to gain a brief speed boost (Disables switching on cooldown)
item.foolish.hands_of_time_greatsword.de: §7Sneak and Right-Click with a free offhand to switch to the dual-wield Minute Form
§7Right-Click without sneaking to start a brief Time Warp, slowing nearby mobs (Disables switching on cooldown)
item.foolish.hyper_stinger.description_0: §7Awards more positive effects to the user and negative effects to the target
item.foolish.incinerator_2.description_0: §7Left-click to shoot a fireball which leaves a trail of flame in its wake
item.foolish.infiltrator_remote.descript: §7Holding it in your hand allows you to mount an Infiltrator
§7Right-click a block to have an Infiltrator fire an explosive beam at it
§7Hit a mob to have an Infiltrator attack it
item.foolish.leaf_fan.description_0: Left-click within the general vicinity of a mob to launch them in the direction you swing.
item.foolish.magnifier.description_0: §7Right-click and hold to fire a laser beam
item.foolish.nether_spear.description_0: §7Right-click to takeoff, hold when midair to move faster and cancel fall damage
item.foolish.nether_spear.description_1: §7Sneak while right-clicking to recharge the spear
item.foolish.parasitic_stinger.descripti: §7Attacking a mob will give regeneration and consume the item
item.foolish.sacilite_charm.description_: §7Right-Click to summon a volley of Seeking Sacilite, targeting nearby mobs. Automatically prioritizes monsters.
item.foolish.sacilite_hammer.description: §7Right-click the ground to perform an AoE attack stunning and damaging nearby mobs.
§7Enemies attacked directly have a chance of being thrown
item.foolish.sandbone_saber_sword.descri: §7Gain a strength boost if you hold one in each hand
item.foolish.scarlant_broadsword.descrip: §7Gives the Offender effect to entities hit. Right-click to summon a random ranking of Scarlant.
item.foolish.scarlant_capsule.descriptio: §7Throw the capsule and the Scarlant inside will attack anything it hits!
item.foolish.scarlant_spade.description_: §7Has a chance to summon a Scarlant from broken blocks
item.foolish.scarlet_saber.description_0: §7Has a chance to give the Offender effect to entities hit, making nearby Scarlants hostile.
item.foolish.scarlet_scepter_staff.descr: §4 Summon your own legions of Scarlants to aid you in battle!
§7 Right click (and hold) to summon different classes of Scarlants when released
§7 15+ Seconds (With Scarlant Crown only)- Scarlant Steed
§7 Any Scarlants above the basic class will have Summoning Sickness, silently damaging them over time.
item.foolish.seven_x_extender.descriptio: §7No building mod? Hate building walls? Extends a block up 7.
item.foolish.starburger.description_1: §7Made from delicious, nutritious, authentic genuine star meat! It's out of this world.
item.foolish.stellar_catalyst.descriptio: §7Summons the Final Boss. Use in an open area which will be destroyed.
item.foolish.thrashing_apparatus.descrip: §7Shake your camera up and down to inflict fall damage
item.foolish.thunderstone_sword.descript: §7Has a chance of striking mobs hit with lightning.
§7The lightning will deal a small amount of damage to you.
item.foolish.triple_threat.description_0: §73 uses, provides all effects with greater durations
item.foolish.voidrider_item.description_: §7Is able to fly for short distances. Land on the ground shortly after flying to do a wheelie, boosting speed.
item.foolish.warp_amber.description_0: §7Obtained by breaking the top of a pulsing Timewood tree
item.foolish.waste_scythe.description_0: §7Has a chance of inflicting poison or corrosion on target
item.foolish.waste_scythe.description_1: §7Right-click to perform an AoE attack which can hit twice
